attributes.Long form description: The student begins by pulling out the paper stand and inserting a paper stack in the printer, then pulls out the tray so he can make a black-and-white copy, the student presses the button on the printer and waits for the copy to finish, when the copy finishes he removes the copy from the printer. Then he changes the ink cartridge and finally pushes the tray and everything left to save the printer.
